P. S. Phantom Blood absolutely destroyed my emotions and I’m not emotionally prepared for Battle Tendency.

summary: The first image is of Priscilla and her ship partner, Tommy! They were quite the pair. I loved RPing with the player - I even...
caption:
The first image is of Priscilla and her ship partner, Tommy! They were quite the pair. I loved RPing with the player - I even made a document to save it so I could read it again in the future. TwT 
The second image is about Priscilla’s past. She used to have a girlfriend who taught her everything she knows about shooting. However, she was murdered by a gang of outlaws that Priscilla’s father hired to go after her.

summary:
Finally got around to lining this SUPER OLD PIECE FROM HIGH SCHOOL!
This was from a comic I was working on called "Casedy-Grace"...
body:
Finally got around to lining this SUPER OLD PIECE FROM HIGH SCHOOL!

This was from a comic I was working on called “Casedy-Grace” and follows Vincent, a middle aged, gay yeti and his adopted half-yeti cub as they escape the human scientists who wiped out their villiage.

Despite the serious overall plot, my later drafts called for a lot of humor and romance.
